Ever think of a naughty practical joke you'd love to play on someone

but wouldn't dare? So have we... lots of times... and we're not

afraid to play them on total strangers. Just for your pleasure,

Playboy TV's hidden camera show takes the practical joke to a whole

new level by adding a titillating twist of sexuality! This outrageous

box set is jam-packed with nearly 2 1/2 hilarious hours of dirty

tricks and hidden camera set-ups on an unsuspecting public. Like...

what if you were hired to answer phones for a day and every visitor

to the office got naked in front of you? Or a woman doing sit-ups in

the park asked you to hold her ankles - and she wasn't wearing any

panties? Then there's Steve-O, who brings his penchant for public

nudity to a New York City pizzeria and a hip Hollywood nightclub.

Even the most jaded patrons get a little shaken up by the sight!
